Class DefaultCommandRoute<I>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.server.route.DefaultCommandRoute<I>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - the type of target entity IDs
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommandRoute<I,io.spine.base.CommandMessage>, Route<io.spine.base.CommandMessage,io.spine.core.CommandContext,I>, Unicast<I,io.spine.base.CommandMessage,io.spine.core.CommandContext>, java.io.Serializable, java.util.function.BiFunction<io.spine.base.CommandMessage,io.spine.core.CommandContext,I>

    public class DefaultCommandRoute<I>
extends java.lang.Object
implements CommandRoute<I,io.spine.base.CommandMessage>
    Obtains a command target entity ID based on a command message and context.

    The command target must be the first field defined in the command message.
